    {
      "id": "l1-colours",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Colours",
      "body": "# Colours\n\n- **Red** (लाल) · **Blue** (नीला) · **Green** (हरा)\n- **Yellow** (पीला) · **Black** (काला) · **White** (सफ़ेद)\n\nIn English the colour word comes **before** the noun: *a red car* (एक लाल गाड़ी), never *a car red*. The colour word never changes for number or gender: *red car*, *red cars*."
    },
